title: Hour 2 - 15yrs Too Long for Juan Soto, Devon Allen
itunes:title: Hour 2 - 15yrs Too Long for Juan Soto, Devon Allen
description:
Dan understands why Juan Soto doesn't want to sign such a long contract. And he talks to Philadelphia Eagles WR and world class hurdler Devon Allen about exactly how fast he really is.
